data.title: Crack CCE 19 FIA CAA Screening
data.meta_description:
Crack CCE 19 FIA CAA Screening - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides notes and tips for preparing for the Sindh Public Service Commission's CCE-2019 screening test. It discusses the following:

1. The test will be held on December 9th, 2018 in various cities across Sindh. It will consist of 100 multiple choice questions covering English, general knowledge, and current affairs. 

2. English questions will test vocabulary, grammar, comprehension and will make up 20% of the test. General knowledge questions will cover Pakistani affairs and make up 80% of the test. 

3. Tips are provided for preparing for the different sections, including practicing past papers, learning word roots for vocabulary, and practicing comprehension by asking questions about passages. Basic
